  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2c9ef64bf8ec0784f88400d1e70391da, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrativeGP.News.NewsController
  gameState: {fileID: 1878978060}
  newsItems:
  - id: 01
    listTitle: '"The Ghost in the Loop": A Fruit Fly Brain Now Lives Inside a Computer'
    displayTitle: '"The Ghost in the Loop": A Fruit Fly Brain Now Lives Inside a
      Computer'
    arrivalDay: 1
    sortOrder: 0
    image: {fileID: -6800377276218365747, guid: 2c25555d4fa3cd74ca5aaecb492c2b8c, type: 3}
    bodyVersions:
    - text: "Researchers this week copied a fruit fly's entire brain into a virtual
        body \u2014 and it works. Building on research from 3 years ago, the digital
        fly now moves, eats, and responds like a real one. \"It can react, but it
        cannot learn,\" said one researcher. The project, funded by NeuroMechA, is
        targeting \"larger organisms\" next."
    - text: "Researchers this week <mark>copied a fruit fly's entire brain into a
        virtual body</mark> \u2014 and it works. Building on research from 3 years
        ago, the digital fly now moves, eats, and responds like a real one. \"It
        can react, but it cannot learn,\" said one researcher. The project, funded
        by NeuroMechA, is targeting \"larger organisms\" next."
    - text: "Researchers this week <mark>copied a fruit fly's entire brain into a
        virtual body</mark> \u2014 and it works. Building on research from 3 years
        ago, the digital fly now moves, eats, and responds like a real one. \"It
        can react, but it cannot learn,\" said one researcher. The project, funded
        by NeuroMechA, is <mark>targeting \"larger organisms\" next</mark>."
  - id: 02
    listTitle: NeuroMechA Responds to Employee Death at Headquarters
    displayTitle: NeuroMechA Responds to Employee Death at Headquarters
    arrivalDay: 2
    sortOrder: 0
    image: {fileID: -6800377276218365747, guid: 2c25555d4fa3cd74ca5aaecb492c2b8c, type: 3}
    bodyVersions:
    - text: Following last week's sudden death of an employee at NeuroMechA's headquarters,
        the company's PR team attributed the incident to "pre-existing personal health
        conditions." A spokesperson stated that the company has "fully complied with
        all labor regulations" and will not be commenting further on internal matters.
    - text: Following last week's sudden death of an employee at NeuroMechA's headquarters,
        the company's PR team attributed the incident to <mark>"pre-existing personal
        health conditions."</mark> A spokesperson stated that the company has "fully
        complied with all labor regulations" and will not be commenting further on
        internal matters.
    - text: Following last week's sudden death of an employee at NeuroMechA's headquarters,
        the company's PR team attributed the incident to <mark>"pre-existing personal
        health conditions."</mark> A spokesperson stated that the company has <mark>"fully
        complied with all labor regulations"</mark> and will not be commenting further
        on internal matters.
  - id: 03
    listTitle: Former NeuroMechA Engineer Sues Over Years of Forced Overtime
    displayTitle: "Former \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
      Engineer Sues Over Years of \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 Overtime"
    arrivalDay: 3
    sortOrder: 0
    image: {fileID: -6800377276218365747, guid: 2c25555d4fa3cd74ca5aaecb492c2b8c, type: 3}
    bodyVersions:
    - text: "A former engineer at \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588,
        identified only as \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588, has filed a \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        against the company, citing years of \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        overtime that destroyed his health. \"I watched people around me \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588,\" he told Sentinel Daily. Other former employees
        are reportedly preparing to join the case."
    - text: "A former engineer at \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588,
        identified only as \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588, has filed a \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        against the company, citing years of \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        <mark>overtime</mark> that destroyed his health. \"I watched people around
        me \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588,\" he told
        Sentinel Daily. Other former employees are reportedly preparing to join the
        case."
  - id: 04
    listTitle: 'Ryan on NeuroMechA Death: "Ben Was a Good Man"'
    displayTitle: "\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 on \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
      Death: \"\u2588\u2588\u2588 \u2588\u2588\u2588 \u2588 Good Man\""
    arrivalDay: 4
    sortOrder: 0
    image: {fileID: -6800377276218365747, guid: 2c25555d4fa3cd74ca5aaecb492c2b8c, type: 3}
    bodyVersions:
    - text: "In a follow-up \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588, former
        engineer \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 was asked about the \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        who died last week. His voice broke. \"His name was \u2588\u2588\u2588. He
        was a good man. He \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588't have
        died like that.\" \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 declined to say more, but added:
        \"I hope someone \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        him. The \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 won't.\""
    - text: "In a follow-up \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588, former
        engineer \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 was asked about the \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        <mark>who died last week</mark>. His voice broke. \"His name was \u2588\u2588\u2588.
        He was a good man. He \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588't
        have died like that.\" \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 declined to say more, but
        added: \"I hope someone \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588
        him. The \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 won't.\""
